## Utils.getDepPath() method

Gets the dep path from start `package` to end `package`<!-- -->. The dep path includes the end `package` but doesn't include the start `package`<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
getDepPath(start: PkgNode, end: PkgNode): PkgNode[];
```

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  start | [PkgNode](./packer.pkgnode.md) | The start <code>package</code> |
|  end | [PkgNode](./packer.pkgnode.md) | The end <code>package</code> |

<b>Returns:</b>

[PkgNode](./packer.pkgnode.md)<!-- -->\[\]
